      <li>Whiting PF, Rutjes AW, Westwood ME, et al. QUADAS-2: a revised tool for the quality assessment of diagnostic accuracy studies. <em>Ann Intern Med</em> 2011;155(8):529–36.</li>
      <li>Sterne JA, Hernán MA, Reeves BC, et al. ROBINS-I: a tool for assessing risk of bias in non-randomised studies of interventions. <em>BMJ</em> 2016;355:i4919.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>
</DocLayout>
